  "slug": "ema-trait-crystallization",
  "title": "If the trait-crystallization test needs a prospective experience diary (not retrospective self-report), could a smartphone-based ecological momentary assessment (EMA) of novel activities during the 6-month follow-up provide the clean measure — and has any personality-change trial used EMA to track the behavioral indicators of openness?",
